{"tid":2035410,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"印度手足又發威，一周內把抖音playstore評分降到1.1星","createTime":"2020-05-26T01:44:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T01:51:59.000Z","uid":267730,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cf725d152262de9b49d46c49af36e3d2326b2702","tid":2035410,"uid":267730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T01:44:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">source 大馬香港議題關注小組</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由來：一個Youtuber 跟一個 Tik Toker 吵架。<br />\n<br />\n1. TikToker 說Youtuber 抄襲，然後賭那個Youtuber不敢嗆他<br />\n<br />\n2. Youtuber 嗆，影片有很多讚跟觀看數<br />\n<br />\n3. 影片被下架，推測是因為TikToker的粉絲回報是&quot;網路霸凌&quot;<br />\n<br />\n4. Youtuber 粉用洗一星回擊<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/2020/05/19/tiktok-rating-plummets-to-2-0-stars-as-an-indian-youtubers-fanbase-orchestrates-one-star-campaign/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.androidpolice.com%2F2020%2F05%2F19%2Ftiktok-rating-plummets-to-2-0-stars-as-an-indian-youtubers-fanbase-orchestrates-one-star-campaign%2F&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY0YD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=72dcbe40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.androidpolice.com/2020/05/19/tiktok-rating-plummets-to-2-0-stars-as-an-indian-youtubers-fanbase-orchestrates-one-star-campaign/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母點解仲有4.3星呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"a6b64b943047e23ffaa04fb0cbc805c1c623e0e2","tid":2035410,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T01:50:29.000Z","msg":"我都上去比1星先 不過太多日本女女用呢個app <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"